He added this morning, though, that he is now homeward bound.

'We are coming home!!!! Flight leaves in around an hour. Can't wait to be back home!' he wrote.

Daley is scheduled to do his pre-games media conferences on Thursday with the diving competition getting under way in Edinburgh on July 30.

The 20-year-old will compete in the 10 metre platform while he has yet to confirm if he and a partner will dive in the 10m synchro.

